overview: UltraMantis and Mister ZERO team up to face BLK OUT in tag team action, but after the match, a startling metamorphosis takes place! and after the match, UltraMantis Black is born! This card features both a "No Disqualification" bout and a "Lumberjack Match" for the I-CROWN (a collection of 6 championships from around the globe!)
title: Chikara: Pick Up or Delivery
